   733	
   734	### Feature Flags
   735	
   736	All flags are evaluated via `isFeatureEnabled()`. After specs 137-139, the 12 original flags default to enabled. Sprint 1-3 (spec 140) added 14 dark-run flags that default to disabled:
   737	
   738	#### Default Enabled (specs 137-139)
   739	
   740	| Flag                         | Default | Description                                                                           |
   741	| ---------------------------- | ------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
   742	| `SPECKIT_RRF`                | `true`  | Enable RRF search fusion                                                              |
   743	| `SPECKIT_MMR`                | `true`  | Enable MMR diversity reranking                                                        |
   744	| `SPECKIT_TRM`                | `true`  | Enable Transparent Reasoning Module (evidence-gap detection)                          |
   745	| `SPECKIT_MULTI_QUERY`        | `true`  | Enable multi-query expansion for deep-mode retrieval                                  |
   746	| `SPECKIT_CROSS_ENCODER`      | `true`  | Enable cross-encoder reranking when a provider is configured (set `false` to disable) |
   747	| `SPECKIT_RELATIONS`          | `true`  | Enable causal memory graph                                                            |
